.TH HIDLOOM-MATRIXD 5 "@HIDLOOM_VERSION@" "HIDloom" "File Formats"
.SH NAME
hidloom-matrixd \- matrixd JSON configuration
.SH DESCRIPTION
The matrixd configuration defines GPIO scan settings, matrix dimensions,
direct switches, rotary encoders, and socket paths used by the native matrix
scanner.
.SH FILES
.TP
.B /usr/lib/hidloom/config/default/matrixd.json
Packaged default configuration.
.TP
.B /mnt/p3
Device-local runtime state directory. Runtime overrides should be documented
and tested before deployment.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR matrixd (8),
.BR logicd (8)
.br
Detailed daemon documentation:
https://github.com/cqa02303/hidloom/tree/@HIDLOOM_GIT_SHA@/docs/daemon
